UID:tXLzW2Ztks1gdYFek7TV2
SUMMARY:First Thursday - June
DTSTAMP:20260413T004304Z
DTSTART:20260604T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Visit MOHAI on the First Thursday of every month for free admis
	sion to the museum’s permanent exhibits between 5—8 pm. \\nFree admission 
	includes access to: True Northwest: The Seattle Journey\\\, Maritime Seatt
	le\\\, Kid-Struction Zone\\\, and the Bezos Center for Innovation\\\, as w
	ell as our temporary display TADAIMA: I’m Home\\\, and our new summer exhi
	bit The Beautiful Game: How Soccer Connects Us All. \\nAdvance online tick
	ets are not required but may be reserved below. \\nMOHAI’s free public acc
